Sounds like you got things working but I&#39;m mildly interested in why you 
had to tinker w/ the eclipse settings.

There is already an entry in the $HERITRIX_HOME/.classpath for src/conf:

...
    &lt;classpathentry kind=&quot;lib&quot; path=&quot;src/conf&quot;/&gt;
...

If I make it an absolute path instead -- i.e. &#39;/src/conf/&#39; instead of 
&#39;src/conf/&#39; -- then eclipse complains &#39;/src/conf/&#39; is missing.

You on windows?  Did you not use the .project and .classpath from 
$HERITRIX_HOME but made your own instead?

Thanks,
